{
  "chapter": 33,
  "chapter_summary": "冷谷双木冷枯木与冷寒竹决定以教裴珏技能的方式继续赌约，约定裴珏若不能在最短时间内学会他们所教的一切便算输。裴珏返回浪莽山庄告知众人赌约详情，檀明欲取消赌约却被战飞、向一啼、那飞虹一致反对。那飞虹提议将赌注寄存于东方五兄弟的飞灵堡。战飞追问檀文琪之事，檀明恼羞成怒以威势相压，战飞则借群豪之势步步紧逼。檀明最终露出本来面目，厉声威胁要让浪莽山庄血流成河，双方剑拔弩张。七巧童子吴鸣世趁乱悄然离去，裴珏独自走出山庄。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "text": "你高兴些什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们既不能与他比武功，也不能白白地饶过他；偏偏他除了不会武功之外，别的也是一窍不通，是么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我真不懂这有什么值得高兴之处！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我此刻却想起了一个两全之策。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "我看你年纪虽轻，但言事甚是诚恳，绝对不会骗人的，是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "text": "在下平生未说一句虚言。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "好，那么你是真的什么也不会的了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "但是我兄弟还是要与你赌一赌，你若输了，便得代你那匆匆而来，匆匆而去的师傅，偿还我们的屈辱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "今后我兄弟两人，要随时随地来教你许多技能；你若不能在最短时间内学会，便算你输了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "text": "真的么？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你且慢点高兴，此事也未见轻易，无论文武两途；琴棋书画、三教九流的技能，只要我兄弟教了你，而你却不能在最短时间中学会，那么你受的罪，绝对要比你想象中重得多。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "这种比试的方法，你可愿意接受？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "那么你从此以后便要跟着我们走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "在下知道！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "浪莽山庄之中，你还有什么事需要料理的么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "text": "那么便请两位在此稍候，在下去去就来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "text": "我总觉得近年来我们实在太寂寞了些，带着这孩子走，实在不错。他无牵无挂，又是个男孩，文琪虽然是个好孩子，只可惜顾忌太多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "不但如此，我们还可以将他自那'神手'战飞的阴谋中救出。你且想想，他们将这样一个少年推出来做江南盟主，这其中岂会没有阴谋？我看这孩子是个可造之才，跟着我们，必定可以学会很多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "text": "其实若论这孩子的生性，和待人处世的方法，他做起绿林道盟主来，实在比别人都好得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "只是他太善良了些，怎比得过那些人的奸狡！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "text": "你可知道，有许多诡计与阴谋，对别人也许有用；但是在仁慈与善良面前，反而会一筹莫展！这就像……这就像……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "这就像冰雪遇着太阳一样，是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "text": "正是，正是，这就像冰雪遇着太阳一样。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大约三年之内，你们还不会知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我也不知道！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "战飞/向一啼/那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "这究竟是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "既然如此，不如将这赌约取消了吧！桌上的那些银子，就算作我送与战庄主的门下好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你那种奇怪的比试，不如取消了吧！与我一齐……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "一言既出，无法取消了！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "正是，一言既出，怎可自悔！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "向一啼/那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "正是，万万反悔不得的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "胜负未分之前，赌约中的珍宝，财物与字据，却应交与一人收寄，谁也不得妄动。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "便连赌约中那十八位兄弟，也不能随意走动，必需与珍宝财物，同被监视，直到胜负分出之后。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位朋友，在下这个意见，可算公平么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此赌法，才有意思！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这可算得上是最最公平的意见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪丙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是这些珍宝之物，应当置于何处呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "东方昆仲威震江湖，'飞灵堡'更是武林圣地之一，东方老堡主威震天下，他五位其中谁也有赌注，但只是随意游戏而已，这些赌注置于'飞灵堡'，也算得是最安全而公平了，各位可说是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "如此说来，那么这位檀姑娘又当怎地？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "她年纪尚轻，方才胡乱所说的话，算不得准的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "她既是胡乱说话，檀老镖头方才为何不加阻止？难道是因为檀老镖头方才有胜算在握，而此刻已无把握，是以便想推赖了么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "数十年来，尚无一人敢对老夫如此说话，战庄主，你莫要忘了老夫对你的客气。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "客气，客气……哈哈，嘿嘿，各位可曾听到这位仁义为先，一诺千金的檀老镖头，方才所说的是什么话么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "向一啼/那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "裴兄留步！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "你这是要做什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "向一啼",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "阁下若是走了，在下等怎能知道胜负如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "我若不走，又怎能分得出胜负？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "胜负分出后，你们自会得到讯息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁敢对盟主无礼？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "向一啼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论如何，我总要差人去跟着他的行踪的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "正是，小弟也有此意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "既是如此，不如你我各派一人跟随于他，也好早些知道胜负。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "檀老镖头意下如何？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "你言语如此傲慢，当真以为老夫已在你势力之下了么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "在下虽然不敢有此意，但目前情况，却似已如此！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "老夫走南闯北，数十年行走江湖，今日难道会毫无准备地来到你这'浪莽山庄'么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "战飞你今日如何将老夫迎入庄来，便得如何将老夫恭送出去；否则老夫便要你这'浪莽山庄'血流成河，化为瓦砾！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 326
